description:
What is globalism? 
World powers are striving to create a unified world that will give them an unprecedented level of control over your life. What does this mean? How can you prepare for it?
In the Book of Genesis we find insight that will help us understand what to expect during the end-time. Satan is working with world leaders to create chaos. destruction, and deception but God warns His people through His word so that they will not be misled. 
How can God's faithful remnant remain true to Him amidst the end-time deceptions? Find out!
